{"tid":777363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實女仔想點","createTime":"2018-08-12T23:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T01:58:30.000Z","uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f00f593a5ac5f3ba1bc559ab0431e6da1bbf063e","tid":777363,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T23:49:13.000Z","msg":"女仔想進一步發展會有咩sign俾到出嚟?<br />\n<br />\n作為男人 應該點樣穩步發展 （唔會太chur 我寧願佛系啲）<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以喺exact嘅moment下啱channel？"},{"pid":"dd92fc81ac5d028a326605447bc4537e413c681e","tid":777363,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:24:09.000Z","msg":"如果你一日都唔主動下<br />\n係可以完全冇Signal <br />\n見你唔郁佢都唔郁 敵不動我不動咁<br />\n不過係針對緊內向嘅女仔"},{"pid":"84d0308b30263d4d0ef34c0505591946ff9e7b0f","tid":777363,"uid":187076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:25:19.000Z","msg":"主動約你"},{"pid":"206059d11a1cc9298be623a8cb11d6485907d1e5","tid":777363,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd92fc81ac5d028a326605447bc4537e413c681e","tid":777363,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:24:09.000Z","msg":"如果你一日都唔主動下<br />\n係可以完全冇Signal <br />\n見你唔郁佢都唔郁 敵不動我不動咁<br />\n不過係針對緊內向嘅女仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:52:15.000Z","msg":"佢係比較主動嘅<br />\n但大家主動嘅方向有少少唔同 <br />\nwhich is可能係件好事<br />\n<br />\n因為有多啲位俾大家入<br />\n佢有兩個姊妹陪住佢所以我唔想搶咗人咁...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 a0"},{"pid":"c18cb7a5e88acc8c6f3c48974c1155b37bd97c3c","tid":777363,"uid":174498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:53:10.000Z","msg":"可能想同你做SP"},{"pid":"d4969bf7c1d076e732dab9d1ec8728fb9ad6d1ec","tid":777363,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"c18cb7a5e88acc8c6f3c48974c1155b37bd97c3c","tid":777363,"uid":174498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:53:10.000Z","msg":"可能想同你做SP"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:59:34.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n<br />\n或者做兵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我做兵ok㗎<br />\n佢個姊妹睇落想收兵多啲 好cute但性格比較港女<br />\n佢就真係好玩得 一開場已經互flirt 火花嚟得好快 但我有個moment冇捉實 <br />\n佢係嗰種比較男人嘅女仔嚟同時又有少少知性嘅味道 樣係差嘅 但作為soul mate已經好好 （咁其實已經唔係男女朋友嗰隻）"},{"pid":"2000ab93c007815746e9fb87cda3e5092e051294","tid":777363,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd92fc81ac5d028a326605447bc4537e413c681e","tid":777363,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:24:09.000Z","msg":"如果你一日都唔主動下<br />\n係可以完全冇Signal <br />\n見你唔郁佢都唔郁 敵不動我不動咁<br />\n不過係針對緊內向嘅女仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:10:17.000Z","msg":"可以點主動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"418228a78214e263508e3f1c9a829796d4b95720","tid":777363,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84d0308b30263d4d0ef34c0505591946ff9e7b0f","tid":777363,"uid":187076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T00:25:19.000Z","msg":"主動約你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:11:18.000Z","msg":"大家約咗大家一年後喺某個location等<br />\n認真"},{"pid":"5cdedf9797b80bb24653d0960b34b22ae81e9f85","tid":777363,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"利申 我哋喺澳洲<br />\n我喺度讀書 佢做緊exchange<br />\n<br />\n識咗三日"},{"pid":"cc80b2e1fe8eaa591695454f148838567a68cd9c","tid":777363,"uid":126615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cdedf9797b80bb24653d0960b34b22ae81e9f85","tid":777363,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"利申 我哋喺澳洲<br />\n我喺度讀書 佢做緊exchange<br />\n<br />\n識咗三日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T01:33:05.000Z","msg":"澳洲邊到<br />\n我都喺澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc397fb4dc7e4d2285fbe1dfb3275d0479d4413","tid":777363,"uid":193476,"li